title: Canada 's biodiesel production 2007 to 2019
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Production in million liters, containing a total of 13 data points.
Overall Production in million liters has increased over the Year.
The steepest increase occurs in between the Year 2013 and 2014.
The highest Production in million liters, of value 463.0 was reached at Year 2016
The lowest Production in million liters, of value 70.0 was reported at Year 2007
